text: Vladislav Yevgenyevich Korobkin (; born 21 June 2000) is a Russian football player. He plays for FC Fakel-M Voronezh. ==Club career== He made his debut in the Russian Football National League for FC Fakel Voronezh on 20 July 2019 in a game against FC Chertanovo Moscow. ==References== ==External links== * Profile by Russian Football National League * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FC Fakel Voronezh players
